
" Theme
set theme dark

" Bind next/prev tab
bind <A-k> tabprev
bind <A-j> tabnext

" Handy multiwindow/multitasking binds
bind gd tabdetach
bind gD composite tabduplicate | tabdetach

" Bind find/find next
bind / fillcmdline find
bind ? fillcmdline find -?
bind n findnext 1
bind N findnext -1
bind ,<Space> nohlsearch

" Bind F2 to help
unbind <F1>
bind <F2> help
